snippet.title: Arsonate - New Buckshot Roulette in Fire / All Endings
snippet.description:
Arsonate - New Buckshot Roulette in Fire / All Endings for the PC in Full HD.
Game Download Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2822980/ARSONATE/

Locked in a FIRE TOWER.
A FOREST FIRE spreads with each flip of a card.
Use UTILITIES to outwit the [HOST].
Be the LAST tower standing.
Do you fear DEATH?
3 possible endings
A game inspired by BUCKSHOT ROULETTE

My name is CatPlay. I'm a big Banban fan and that's why I made this channel for you. On my channel you can see exceptional new mods for my favorite game. Every day I try to please you with new videos and I will be glad if you support me by subscribing and viewing my videos :3
